It introduces the following concepts:
@table @code
@item enum status @{A, B, C@}
User defined @code{enum} type named @code{status},
@item [s.A]
Field test of enum variable @code{s}: evaluates to @code{true} if
@code{s} has field value @code{A}, it is equivalent to @code{s ==
status.A},
@item [s.B || s.C]
Logical or @code{||} in guard expression (see @xref{Expressions}),
